hackathon-rules:
No atendees may harass or discriminate against any protected class, as listed in the Anime In Northwest Ohio Constitution.
All attendees are expected to act civily as they would at any university function. There will be no fighting over Text Editors or Waifus. Failure to do so will result in expulsion.
